name: Uint32Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of Uint32Array.

name: Uint32Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of a Uint32Array.

name: Uint32Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Uint32Array instances, the initial value is the Uint32Array constructor.
